&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2014-12-27 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-3694/log-12194/"&gt;Ready to Program&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
