&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2017-01-11 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-6050/log-51725/"&gt;New Year Reflections&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
