&lt;li class="ablog-post"&gt;&lt;p class="ablog-post-title"&gt;2016-11-10 - &lt;a class="reference internal" href="../../../projects/project-6050/log-48901/"&gt;Pimp Your Robot II&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
